title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - December 2, 2021

description:
Gary & Mark connect to give an update on the current case captivating the Supreme Court and what it may mean for the future of abortion law. 

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
